@HR key @HC key @deleted-role As the end of the year approaches, I am going to try out some drastic changes to prepare us for the long year ahead. A change to the Quota system Probably the most controversial one, Glitchy might shout at me for this. But I want to make changes to the quota system we have here. Taking advice from the Black Marines, I wanted to try using the points system to complete the weekly quota. How it works The points system assigns a value of hosting different events.
